Adjust rack to top position and preheat #oven{} to 425 degrees.

Slice @demi-baguette{1} crosswise into 8 rounds. Spread slices out on a #baking sheet{}, drizzle with @olive oil{1%tablespoon}, and season with @salt{} and @pepper{}. Toast on top rack of oven until golden brown, ~{5-10%minutes}.

Meanwhile, slice @mozzarella cheese{4%ounce} into 8 rounds.

Arrange mozzarella and @prosciutto{2%ounce} on a #serving board{}. Drizzle both with @Mike's Hot Honey{3}. Serve with toasted baguettes on the side.

